One of our Paladins on the Povar server has finally done the complete suit of the Armor of Ro. Besides the arms and the gauntlets, the suit basically pulled a Star Wars: TPM, not worth the wait or hype. :-)<BR>
<BR>
* You need a Mastery Smithing skill of at least 175, but he said he did succeed on the first try at about 150, but then failed since then. You ONLY need the Smithing skill to make the Ronium.<BR>
<BR>
* The armor is not a steel/silver plated look appearance, its very white with a tint of pink.
